column3: To my side, Enkidu! The battle is joined!
Owww! It hurts! It hurts!Enkidu! Your master wants for succor!
Fancy some feathers...bird brain?
This should cut you down to size...
Fight on, Enkidu, my ever faithful\xe2\x94\x80hm!?
Enkidu! Are the bonds of our friendship so fragile!?
Not the \x02\x1a\x02\x02\x03strongest\x02\x1a\x02\x01\x03 of swords, but it should suffice.
Gilgamesh is in the mood...for dancing!
Divide and conquer, Gilgamesh style!
...And now for something truly \x02\x1a\x02\x02\x03shocking\x02\x1a\x02\x01\x03!
What's the matter, friend? All tied up?
Uh-oh! Someone just woke the dragon...
You have some skill, I'll give you that...\x02\x10\x01\x03But Gilgamesh has only just begun to fight!
Most impressive!\x02\x10\x01\x03Very well\xe2\x94\x80I, too, shall fight with all my strength!
No! The mighty Gilgamesh will not be defeated!
At long last, we meet again on the battlefield!\x02\x10\x01\x03I daresay Enkidu shall come to enjoy our tussles as much as I.
\x02\x1a\x02\x02\x03You\x02\x1a\x02\x01\x03, however, might not find this one so enjoyable.\x02\x10\x01\x03...Unless you enjoy getting pounded senseless. Hah!
\x02\x1a\x02\x02\x03Me\x02\x1a\x02\x01\x03? Run away? Hah! I-I was but seeking out a\x02\x10\x01\x03more suitable spot to celebrate my inevitable victory!
But enough exposition! Now we fight like men!\x02\x10\x01\x03And ladies! And ladies who dress like men!
For Gilgamesh...it is transmogrifying time!
The mightiest warrior ever to grace Eorzea stands before you\xe2\x94\x80\x02\x10\x01\x03by which I mean \x02\x1a\x02\x02\x03I\x02\x1a\x02\x01\x03, Gilgamesh! Prepare yourself!
To think that my full complement of arms would avail me naught...
No more high jinks from Gilgamesh. You have my word.
The Treaty-Blade, too, I shall return.\x02\x10\x01\x03...Just as soon as I remember where I hid it.
Anyway, I yield to your unparalleled puissance!\x02\x10\x01\x03Spare my insignificant life, I beg of you!
...NOT! Ha, I lied...again! Like a rug! Oh, I kill me!
You can take that fusty old blade for all I care! I thirst for \x02\x1a\x02\x02\x03true\x02\x1a\x02\x01\x03\x02\x10\x01\x03power, and naught save the strongest of swords will suffice!
Warrior of Light\xe2\x94\x80you have proven a worthy opponent.\x02\x10\x01\x03But I warn you\xe2\x94\x80treasure every moment with your weapon.
For as sure as day follows night, the hour will come when\x02\x10\x01\x03I claim it as mine own! Till we meet again!
